        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Go for prenerf CoS</P><P>Scaiiz you must be joking, the prenerf is THE item a necro must have, and 10k is really worth it, saved my butt hundreds of time:</P><P>1-you're in a KoS zone with hard beaters (like 20 mobs hitting for 100+ on your path), they don't see invis. Invis begins to drop while you're in.<BR>you have a prenerf? clic on it, instant invis, no agro<BR>you don't have it? cast invis, invis drops, you stay 3 seconds with no invis, you aggro, you die</P><P>2-you're in a KoS zone (with mobs not seeing invis), kitting for example. you get adds, you FD, when you stand up you have 7/10 chances that the mobs will come back to wipe your ass (at 50+ though)<BR>now if you stand up and insta clic prenerf, you go invis and mobs don't re-agro cause the indif of FD will become a invis indif, and you'll be mem wiped.</P><P>you should definitly go for a prenerf CoS, changed my life far more than the jboots (+ at level 20 you don't really need run speed, i think the ability of going through higher lvl zones is far more important)<BR>staff of the dreaded gaze... well... fun toy, but not really sure it's so usefull, it's true the 1st fear sucks, but when you get invoke fear (spell the wand casts, but with far more casting time) you'll need fast cast, not free cast... (or i would be stuck at 1st fear, nearly no cost)</P><P>Masklinn Papeteri<BR>Heretic from Morell Thule</font></td>
